SUMMARY:BayCare Presents - Suicide Awareness: How to Check in with a Frien
 d
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Starting a conversation about suicide can feel overwhelming\, 
 but it can also save a life. This presentation focuses on practical\, empa
 thetic strategies for checking in with someone who may be struggling. Well
  explore warning signs\, how to approach the conversation with care\, and 
 what resources are available for support. By learning how to listen withou
 t judgment and respond effectively\, you can make a meaningful difference 
 when it matters most. Click here to join the meeting (https:teams.microsof
 t.commeet23063052043892?pUK85nDaqLcOq2Zt3aD) \n\nPermalink: https://www.ta
 mpa.gov/node/178721
